ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Trainin Brass
ygData.msgSnippet: Go to Arena, start it up, and go to the mall.  :) I have also watched a movie, within sight of the computer, just in case, while parked on a zone wall with it
ygData.messageBody:
Go to Arena, start it up, and go to the mall. :)

I have also watched a movie, within sight of the computer, just in case,
while parked on a zone wall with it playing.

Kunark zone walls aren't all that safe, but a lot of Antonica zone walls are
fairly safe, up high, in a corner. You still want to keep an eye on it,
though.

Atonal
